  "texts": [
    "We adopt the strategy first to handle the temporal and spatial dimensions.",
    "Thus, we implement the encoder network with a 1D version of backbone networks for extracting temporal information.",
    "Two 2D-CNN layers are followed to extract spatial information.",
    "Besides the previously tested networks, including the 1D version of stacked CNN (like VGG) and ResNet, we also tested a 1D version of DenseNet.",
    "The application of the 2D-convolutional layer for spatial information relies on the regular distribution of sensors."
